<div class="uk-width-small-1-1 uk-width-medium-1-3">
<h3>Internship only</h3>
<p>This includes the placement for your internship in China. It's recommended for young professionals and students that are already in China, have been in China before or know someone in the city. This program includes an internship in China, Hong Kong or Singapore within your field of interest, predefined in the minutes of the Skype call that you will have with a member of the IntuuChina staff. After being placed, our offices will be open to answer any of your questions and doubts about your internship in China. You will also be subscribed to our monthly newsletters on events and job openings, though you won't have any discount on the entrance of such events.</p>
</div>
<div class="uk-width-small-1-1 uk-width-medium-1-3">
<h3>Relocation Services</h3>
<p>If you're looking into moving to China this package will ease your transition. With these sufficient relocation services and the help of our local office manager, you can move to Shanghai and start experiencing China stress-free with the most time-consuming procedures taken care of by us! This is the recommended add-on for those who have never been in China or don't know anyone here. This service is only available if you are doing the internship in Shanghai, but will be available in other cities of China, Hong Kong and Singapore soon. This program starts the 23rd and 24th of every month and lasts for three to six months in accordance with your internship in China.</p>
</div>
<div class="uk-width-small-1-1 uk-width-medium-1-3">
<h3>Full Immersion Internship Program</h3>
<p>For those who want the full experience with their internship, we offer the Full Immersion Program. Under this program we provide you with accommodation in a modern, comfortable apartment with other interns and students as flat mates. We organize weekly trips and activities to acquaint you with Chinese culture, history, cuisine and landmarks &ndash; all accompanied by our competent and friendly staff. We help you with the practical matters for your visa, arrival in China and first days while you get used to your new surroundings. In short, this program is for you if you are looking for an all-inclusive program to ensure that your time in China will be truly unforgettable.</p>
</div>
